caller_intent: Angela Fulton wants to add a car to her existing personal car insurance policy.
resolution_steps: Agent confirmed the policy is personal.
Agent requested time to consider recent changes to the policy.
Agent prepared to transfer the call to a specialist.
knowledge_required: Process for adding vehicles to existing policies
systems_referenced: Alliance Insurance internal call routing system
summary: Angela requested to add a vehicle to her personal car insurance policy. The agent confirmed the policy type and began assessing recent changes before preparing to transfer the call to a specialist. The conversation was cut off mid-escalation.
